Run

```
git clone https://github.com/adabru/dovecot_postfix.git
cd dovecot_postfix
docker build -t mail .

# get inside the container:
docker run --rm --name test -ti -p 465:465 -p 993:993 mail /bin/sh

# test global connectivity in both directions
ping adabru.de
nc -v -l -p 993

syslogd
postfix start
```
